_sText:
My first map
Just finding out how to use Hammer
Default lighting
2 Bombsites, but I couldn't get env_explosion to work - any help will be appreciated.
Breakable crates
Buyzones
2 Sniper towers
All in one room

Please comment - I'd like to find out how I can improve my work
If you think it's no good please tell me, I want to make maps other people will enjoy playing
Feel free to decompile and edit - I don't mind if other people improve or modify my maps.

I will soon be starting work on an improved version of aim_fort for CSS with top and underground floors, hidden rooms and extra features. I would like to find a copy of the original CSS aim_fort to work from, please tell me if you find one.

~MyKill~
